'''Civic 10''' ({{lang-it|Movimento Civico10}}) is a political party in [[San Marino]]. It advocates [[democratic socialism]], [[environmentalism]], [[E-democracy]] and opposition to [[particracy]].

==History==
The party was established on 30 July 2012 and contested the [[Sammarinese general election, 2012|2012 general elections]] as part of the [[Active Citizenship]] alliance. It received 6.7% of the vote and winning four seats.<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/1644/ San Marino] IFES</ref>

The party is against San Marino joining the [[European Union]].

