'''Dajbabe''' is a [[Serbian Orthodox]] Christian [[Monastery]] in [[Podgorica]], [[Montenegro]]. It is located in a cave on [[Dajbabe hill]] (''Dajbabska gora''), which raises above [[Zeta valley]]. The monastery was founded in 1897.

